git-cola: 1.4.0.4
bottled-on: Sat Nov 14 11:00:41 PST 2009

commit a4abb434f60f023ff39a4d47bca0d14f9708b91c (HEAD, tag: v1.4.0.4, maint-1.4.0)
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Nov 13 23:52:54 2009 -0800

    doc: Add git-cola-1.4.0.4 release notes
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 3a26c5cee006712a18ac2e9924548cb72a9c32e6
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Nov 13 22:35:37 2009 -0800

    Move SSH_ASKPASS scripts to share/git-cola/bin
    
    This fixes Lintian warnings by removing the non-standard
    /usr/libexec directory.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit c922a3390c6e4a4512d688681cafc6a933f2ee2d (tag: v1.4.0.3)
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Nov 9 16:03:47 2009 -0800

    doc: Add git-cola-1.4.0.3 release notes
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 8d59660cf990dd7a60807e09143d1250d88d8113
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Nov 9 14:57:25 2009 -0800

    views.status: Eliminate X11 warnings
    
    Expanding childless top-level items causes X11 warnings to appear
    in the shell.  This was happening because we were looping over
    each top-level item inside of expand_items().
    
    expand_items() now expands the item passed into it only.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 7ad83e82d0ede867131550253cf7b4d1565a249c (tag: v1.4.0.2)
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 5 18:39:54 2009 -0800

    doc: Add git-cola-1.4.0.2 release notes
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 259b150f9189e4877b47f9a59bb3c14b253625ab
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 5 09:14:05 2009 -0800

    models.main: Guard against non-int font sizes
    
    The cola.fontdiff setting can contain non-integer
    font sizes, so guard against it by casting to a float
    before casting to int.
    
    Closes #32
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit ee17ea12d8a4dc9987364867637025e59a93d087
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 5 09:20:29 2009 -0800

    views.main: Show 'Exit Diff Mode' when using Diff->Expression
    
    We weren't showing the 'Exit Diff Mode' button when going into
    the 'Diff->Expression' mode.
    
    Closes #31
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 22355e51d3d52826166269e70a8bf3710c590f59 (tag: v1.4.0.1)
