commit 1d8fb7871b8816db3e34f7d793ef448a3b4d55a1
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Oct 11 17:00:22 2009 -0700

    cola.version: Pass --match when using git-describe
    
    This ensures that we only find tags matching the v$VERSION
    major.minor.micro.patch naming convention.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

