commit 90dd7199de1ea421647fe50f79fec9ac6c3d6e08
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Sep 18 03:19:21 2009 -0700

    cmdfactory: Observe the 'current_text' model attribute
    
