Date:   Tue Sep 1 02:06:44 2009 -0700

    cola.git: Remove mentions of 'input'
    
    This renames the 'input' variable used in 'shell_quote' to avoid
    using the same name as the Python builtin.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 13cc9f3e9aef27d4d4585ca5d07744f0cef2dffd
