commit 47bff97d9bf688edd487b92f8621f2a018b828e7
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Aug 19 16:36:17 2009 -0700

    cola.models.main: Properly handle renames
    
    Instead of trying to parse the rename information,
    simply ignore renames and treat them like an add and
    remove, which is exactly what the GUI wants to display
    anyways.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 6963e486311227f03f3c8539465bd8f983cde020
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
