Date:   Wed Jun 24 23:10:12 2009 -1000

    views/repo: change the 'View History...' shortcut to avoid clashes
    
    Cmd+H is 'Hide' on Mac OS X.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 4eb65529f2437847d8cc70c03ec2444d1051a161
