commit 7d82503e6d979cae4780e637859ffa3c64ca371b
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 24 18:14:40 2009 -1000

    models/classic: add a 'revert_paths' method
    
    'revert_paths' removes local changes by reverting file paths back to
    their content in the latest commit.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit d9005f16538c828ecf763f35b4382f2bb5eb6cfa
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 24 18:11:55 2009 -1000

    classic: allow difftool to be run on multiple paths
    
    The 'View Diff...' action now accepts multiple paths.
    We can now select a directory or multi-select individual items
    in the treeview when launching difftool.
    
