commit 56d10d420c3c47980d8e4791547b0a51a532289f
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 23 21:18:43 2009 -1000

    models/classic: add an 'everything' method to return all files
    
    'everything' returns the combined output of 'git ls-files' and
    'git ls-files --others --exclude-standard' in a sorted list.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit b6a59881fd28419f210feda5348db71f326b5a0d
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 23 21:14:26 2009 -1000

    classic: use observation for handling updates to 'staged' files.
    
    The controller no longer modifies the view directly.
    Instead, the view registers for the 'paths_staged' message
    from the model and reacts accordingly.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

