commit cbeae4ef7b1217004a15ccdff5ff3db9195161eb
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jun 15 02:59:09 2009 -0700

    classic: move model initialization code into the model itself
    
    The (currently empty) controller knew too much about the model's
    internals, so refactor that knowledge it into the model itself.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 99e6dfbc0076115e86eb9acf7f28c6c8457cafb4
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat May 2 16:56:54 2009 -0700

    controllers: add a 'classic' module to implement a tkcvs-like view
    
    Users have often asked to see the status of their entire project.
    The 'classic' controller provides this behavior.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 5ca3c53ccde21205ff74857b9681d8ee58ee0dd9
