commit 455f394f0dc138e76b0e770995f29d8305e5d7df
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Apr 24 03:58:18 2009 -0700

    ui: add a Branch->Review action for reviewing in-progress branches
    
    Branch->Review compares a branch against its common ancestor
    with the current branch.  This basically shows you what's
    in a branch and lets you run difftool on it.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 0f25ad250b736a25349f2466ae892ea0421e9e99
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 22 16:02:09 2009 -0700

    remote: select the current branch by default for 'push'
    
    'git push' now requires both the remote and branch to be specified when pushing,
    so select the current branch by default since that is the typical use case.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 673da3cd3cd86de7e1f9bacd69723cbb16ed9df4
