    views/remote: hide appropriate controls when in specific fetch/push/pull modes
    
    This makes the remote gui automatically hide controls based on its mode.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit a138c60dc55f59e56ace3498074226ae78df3a4d
