commit 61cff60a6970afbed3c3cd3922303b18edb891a8
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 17 01:03:41 2009 -0700

    json: make cola's pickle module exception-safe
    
    cola.jsonpickle wasn't exception-safe and was breaking
    help('modules').
    
    This fixes Debian bug #519971.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

