Date:   Sat Feb 7 19:15:13 2009 -0800

    controllers: refactor the init() method out of the controllers api
    
    We no longer use the init() stuff so subclasses just override __init__ now.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 504012ac092ccb43d556174b9293c7ab2a22b4cf
