commit 44a508004d5c41a6924aa996613c11caee23e708
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Dec 26 19:23:48 2008 -0800

    views: remove exec_ calls so that all dialogs are non-modal
    
    Calling exec_ makes it so that the parent window cannot be
    raised above the child window.  This removes all exec()
    calls to prevent this.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

