Date:   Thu Nov 13 23:04:23 2008 -0800

    models: do not list a file in both the unmerged and modified sections
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit eca3d33342076104ad544405eab55808837b9a4c
