commit cd6ad92fb5e358731ab012e5ae722be66062eaff
Merge: 761314e 786132c
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Jul 9 02:20:23 2008 -0700

    Merge branch 'master' into release
    
